      <t>&lt;p&gt;This memo defines a series of metrics for connectivity between a pair of Internet hosts.  It builds on notions introduced and discussed in RFC 2330, the IPPM framework document.  This memo defines an Experimental Protocol for the Internet community.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
